a5d35b30b60f3ca71f4aeefc4596db59c14b6da5.summary: US forces captured Venezuelan president Nicolas Maduro and brought him to New York to face federal drug charges. Donald Trump said the US is 'in charge' of Venezuela and warned interim president Delcy Rodríguez to cooperate or face further action. The US plans to use an oil blockade to pressure change, while the UN Security Council is meeting on the situation.
a5d35b30b60f3ca71f4aeefc4596db59c14b6da5.headline: US Detains Maduro Trump Claims Control Over Venezuela

45a3720f4b429d16f9230ee7f4d96408ff76f2cd.summary: U.S. forces have captured Venezuela's president Nicolas Maduro and his wife, Cilia Flores, following an attack. Venezuela's interim president Delcy Rodriguez has met with the cabinet of ministers. Gold prices surged 64% last year amid geopolitical tensions and the recent events in Venezuela.
45a3720f4b429d16f9230ee7f4d96408ff76f2cd.headline: U.S. Captures Venezuela President Maduro

ea8bad99f79c9ec727f9af2b0d96cd8ff276217d.summary: Cuba reports that 32 of its armed forces or interior ministry officers were killed during a U.S. operation in Venezuela that resulted in the arrest of Nicolas Maduro. Havana has declared two days of mourning for the Cuban casualties. The raid also reportedly killed much of Maduro's security team.
ea8bad99f79c9ec727f9af2b0d96cd8ff276217d.headline: Cuba Mourns 32 Officers Killed in U.S. Operation Arresting Maduro

d4e2910ffd1102b0978fb1811bfd5cb2515b3da1.summary: The Las Vegas Raiders have secured the first overall pick in the 2026 NFL Draft after finishing 3-14 and winning a tiebreaker among four teams with the same record. The Jets and Cardinals hold the second and third picks, while the Giants are set to pick fifth after a 4-13 season.
d4e2910ffd1102b0978fb1811bfd5cb2515b3da1.headline: Raiders Secure First Pick in 2026 NFL Draft

71d6b7743d6d04a5a2c647db2c50d6cf2e388b34.summary: Swiss police have identified all 40 people killed in the New Year's Eve bar fire at Crans-Montana, with over half of the victims under 18, including two aged 14. A day of mourning is planned for Friday, and a criminal investigation is ongoing.
71d6b7743d6d04a5a2c647db2c50d6cf2e388b34.headline: All Victims Identified in Crans Montana Bar Fire

807d36140ee6bce69c7f503726b295efdf663d6d.summary: Cleveland Browns defensive end Myles Garrett set the NFL single-season sack record with his 23rd sack during a 20-18 win over the Cincinnati Bengals. Garrett achieved the record by sacking Bengals quarterback Joe Burrow late in the fourth quarter of the season finale.
807d36140ee6bce69c7f503726b295efdf663d6d.headline: Myles Garrett Sets NFL Single Season Sack Record With 23 Sacks

6e536e24ce108ad5512fa871a82566706f2895e9.summary: Donald Trump's proposal to take control of and revitalize Venezuela's oil industry is facing significant challenges, including deteriorating infrastructure and unclear leadership in the country.
6e536e24ce108ad5512fa871a82566706f2895e9.headline: Trumps Venezuela Oil Plan Encounters Major Obstacles

cd1410455e6473d9b1ccc35d8dd3c57065bc3017.summary: The Pittsburgh Steelers won the AFC North title by defeating the Baltimore Ravens after Baltimore's Tyler Loop missed a 44-yard field goal in the final seconds of their Week 18 game.
cd1410455e6473d9b1ccc35d8dd3c57065bc3017.headline: Steelers Win AFC North After Ravens Miss Late Field Goal

464279de3e3e585ee533ca10d7d3f22ff7006658.summary: The Atlanta Falcons have fired head coach Raheem Morris and general manager Terry Fontenot after two consecutive disappointing seasons.
464279de3e3e585ee533ca10d7d3f22ff7006658.headline: Falcons Dismiss Raheem Morris and Terry Fontenot After Two Seasons

f30f07249cf183ea0c4dfcc8352cf32434fe2544.summary: Devin Booker made a game-winning three-pointer with 0.7 seconds left, leading the Phoenix Suns to a 108-105 victory over the Oklahoma City Thunder.
f30f07249cf183ea0c4dfcc8352cf32434fe2544.headline: Devin Bookers Last Second Three Lifts Suns Over Thunder

a243d0298c4f5d30b12cd33df33d0b0e96244a93.summary: Venezuelan President Nicolas Maduro, captured by U.S. forces on Saturday, is scheduled to make his first federal court appearance in New York City on Monday to face federal criminal charges.
a243d0298c4f5d30b12cd33df33d0b0e96244a93.headline: Maduro to Appear in U.S. Federal Court Monday on Criminal Charges

2e56030c909868ffde9f7f7bda7a7d3bcc27fc01.summary: The UN Security Council will discuss the US abduction of Nicolás Maduro and his wife after President Trump ordered an attack that resulted in their capture. Trump stated he may order further action if Venezuela does not cooperate with US efforts to open its oil industry and curb drug trafficking.
2e56030c909868ffde9f7f7bda7a7d3bcc27fc01.headline: UN Security Council to Address US Capture of Maduro and Wife

51ce9514fbb690e43793219a2c0de7265f624d3c.summary: Luka Doncic scored 36 points with nine rebounds and eight assists, and LeBron James added 26 points with 10 assists as the Los Angeles Lakers defeated the Memphis Grizzlies 120-114. The Lakers have beaten Memphis twice in three days.
51ce9514fbb690e43793219a2c0de7265f624d3c.headline: Lakers Defeat Grizzlies Again Behind Doncic and James

6492c0b7ddb2c44c103cb2eb54d882fa11e50f3c.summary: The US president has expressed a desire for the island to become part of the US, prompting officials from the island to reject the idea and urge the US to respect their decision.
6492c0b7ddb2c44c103cb2eb54d882fa11e50f3c.headline: Island Officials Reject US Presidents Proposal for Annexation

6f93ad3bf1595f35988482d7dfcc2d8f845e51ba.summary: Rights groups report that at least 16 people have died in Iran during a week of protests, according to multiple sources.
6f93ad3bf1595f35988482d7dfcc2d8f845e51ba.headline: At Least 16 Dead in Iran During Week of Protests

f0e6d6aa15395d2834daf7ee39d7dccf4c4c99c3.summary: Real Madrid have shown interest in signing Crystal Palace midfielder Adam Wharton. Crystal Palace are considering their options while AC Milan are monitoring Nathan Ake.
f0e6d6aa15395d2834daf7ee39d7dccf4c4c99c3.headline: Real Madrid Interested in Crystal Palaces Adam Wharton

e7eebc08f30d4b53f436435fcfe77006a3b40596.summary: Czechia defeated Canada in the world juniors semifinal, eliminating Canada from gold medal contention for the third consecutive year.
e7eebc08f30d4b53f436435fcfe77006a3b40596.headline: Czechia Eliminates Canada in World Juniors Semifinal

e51124c353c924c1f33f7713c8a6bc38c03ffd34.summary: Trump stated that the US may conduct a second strike on Venezuela if the Venezuelan government does not cooperate.
e51124c353c924c1f33f7713c8a6bc38c03ffd34.headline: Trump Warns of Possible Second US Strike on Venezuela

b6c64e28cb4e4604ca1e7d89579a65fc5ccdbb01.summary: US oil refiners have benefited while Chinese competitors lost out following US action in Venezuela. The capture of Venezuela's president Nicolás Maduro by the US has led to short-term export disruptions, and oil prices have fallen due to concerns over a potential increase in global supply.
b6c64e28cb4e4604ca1e7d89579a65fc5ccdbb01.headline: US Actions in Venezuela Affect Oil Markets and Global Supply

e58551de53009dc7b043caba233aea82a35449db.summary: North Korean state media reported that Kim Jong Un oversaw a hypersonic missile test and emphasized the need to strengthen North Korea's nuclear deterrent, citing a recent geopolitical crisis.
e58551de53009dc7b043caba233aea82a35449db.headline: Kim Jong Un Oversees North Korean Hypersonic Missile Test

d59c4b10a458d2fefe842a0127277bacd389315c.summary: Trump has warned that the U.S. may impose higher tariffs on India due to its ongoing purchases of Russian oil. India has defended its imports, citing the need for domestic energy security. The warning follows increased attention in Washington to India's energy trade with Russia.
d59c4b10a458d2fefe842a0127277bacd389315c.headline: Trump Warns India of Higher Tariffs Over Russian Oil Imports

107f101a4264eb682da23107ac9f6772fad2c495.summary: Investors are closely monitoring recent developments in Venezuela for potential impacts on global markets. Alongside this, markets are awaiting key economic data releases, including a jobs report and earnings reports, which could influence market movements this week.
107f101a4264eb682da23107ac9f6772fad2c495.headline: Investors Monitor Venezuela and Key Economic Data for Market Impact

85f054cf5e9260fd2ddefec4ff9ee7d3d4aa2560.summary: The United States has captured Nicolás Maduro. The move has led to a surge in Venezuelan government bond prices and a rise in Bitcoin value, while oil prices have declined. The legality of Maduro's capture is being discussed at the United Nations, and the event is testing the limits of China's diplomatic efforts.
85f054cf5e9260fd2ddefec4ff9ee7d3d4aa2560.headline: US Captures Maduro Markets React

84494329bb582cc106587ec916c39fdf1e76cd80.summary: U.S. authorities have arrested Nicolás Maduro, citing the Monroe Doctrine as part of their justification. The doctrine, a longstanding U.S. policy opposing foreign intervention in the Americas, has been referenced in discussions about the arrest's legal and diplomatic basis.
84494329bb582cc106587ec916c39fdf1e76cd80.headline: U.S. Cites Monroe Doctrine in Nicolás Maduro Arrest

24abc0a1eb467af6cc953d61825612c084f86ecb.summary: Venezuela's defense minister stated that a large part of Nicolás Maduro's security team was killed in a U.S. action. No further details about the incident or casualties were provided in the available reports.
24abc0a1eb467af6cc953d61825612c084f86ecb.headline: Venezuela Says US Action Killed Much of Maduros Security Team

3d6be82adf9c68c53176a18b3b222466789d4602.summary: Photos show damage in Venezuela following US airstrikes. North Korea has condemned the US strikes, calling them a serious violation of Venezuela's sovereignty.
3d6be82adf9c68c53176a18b3b222466789d4602.headline: US Airstrikes Hit Venezuela
